| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6841 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e7ab081d-83a2-565e-a8d0-a4f7b783847c"
